.SH NAME
edp \- Electronic Density Plotter
.SH SYNOPSIS
edp -i [chgcar] -v [v1,v2,v3] -w [w1,w2,w3] -p [p1,p2,p3] -o [plot.png]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Electron density plotter is a tiny tool for generating electron density plots from VASP output.
.SH OPTIONS
.IP "-i chgcar"
Input file (chgcar)
.IP "-v v1,v2,v3"
Direction vector 1
.IP "-w w1,w2,w3"
Direction vector 2
.IP "-p p1,p2,p3"
3D vector for a point in the unit cell or a single number for an atom position
.IP "-o plot.png"
Output file
.SH EXAMPLE
edp -i CHGCAR -v 1-2 -w 0,0,1 -p 1 -o plot.png
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
